This repository contains my learning journey towards becoming an Agentic AI Engineer.

 Project 1: Gemini Chatbot
 Description

A simple AI chatbot built using Google's Gemini API and Python.

### Features

* Accepts user input
* Sends prompts to Gemini
* Generates AI-powered responses
* Interactive chatbot experience

### Technologies Used

* Python
* Google Gemini API
* Jupyter Notebook

### Skills Learned

* API Integration
* Prompt Engineering
* LLM Fundamentals
* Python Programming

